snippet.title: I'm Back - Indie Devlog 20 #indiegame #gamedev
snippet.description:
It's been a few months since I've done a dedicated video - but I'm back. Kickstarter preparation and running of the campaign has been intense. Let's talk about that and We Are Not Alone as a whole.

!! Check out the awesome rewards available!! 
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wearenotalone/we-are-not-alone-1/
